<p>For assistance using the online licensing system, please see the <a title="Frequently Asked Questions about Online Licensing" href="http://www.dshs.state.tx.us/avc/online-licensing-faq.aspx">Frequently Asked Questions about Online Licensing</a> webpage.</p>
